## Shop

- [All Products]({{ store_url }}/collections/all): The complete Aliangé clinical skincare range — serums, masques, cleansers, day and night creams, and protocol systems. Formulated by Dr. Alison Jamieson. Australian made.
- [Skincare Protocols]({{ store_url }}/collections/protocols): Complete doctor-designed skincare systems targeting ageing, pigmentation, breakouts, and more. Each protocol sequences products in three phases — Prepare & Purify, Stimulate & Communicate, Protect & Fortify — for histological skin change.
- [Clinical Serums]({{ store_url }}/collections/serums): Highly concentrated serums featuring exosomes, jellyfish peptides, sphingolipids, and Oligopeptide-68. Targets cellular repair, collagen synthesis, pigmentation, and hydration. Applied after cleansing, before creams.
- [Skincare Masques]({{ store_url }}/collections/masques): Intensive treatment masques using probiotic complexes and antioxidant blends to purify, restore the skin microbiome, and deeply hydrate. Recommended 2–3 times per week.
- [Cleansers & Exfoliators]({{ store_url }}/collections/cleanse): Amino acid and coconut-derived cleansers and AHA/BHA exfoliators that prepare a balanced cellular canvas without disrupting the skin's acid mantle or lipid barrier.
- [Gift Cards]({{ store_url }}/collections/gift-cards): Aliangé digital gift cards — the perfect introduction to doctor-led clinical skincare. Delivered by email, no expiry.

