## Skin Concerns & Clinical Education

- [Anti-Ageing Skincare Guide]({{ store_url }}/pages/concern-aging): Doctor-led clinical guide to the science of skin ageing — collagen loss, cellular senescence, photoageing — and the Aliangé multi-pathway protocol for visibly rejuvenated, firmer skin. Includes timeline of results and clinical data.
- [Pigmentation & Dark Spots Guide]({{ store_url }}/pages/concern-pigmentation): Clinical explanation of hyperpigmentation, melasma, and post-inflammatory pigmentation. Covers how Aliangé's brightening actives — Oligopeptide-68, multi-acid resurfacing, and Vitamin C — address the root causes of uneven skin tone.
- [Breakouts & Acne Guide]({{ store_url }}/pages/concern-breakouts): Doctor-led guide to acne and congested skin — comedones, hormonal breakouts, inflamed lesions — and the Aliangé clinical approach to clearing pores, reducing inflammation, and preventing recurrence.
- [Dull Skin & Radiance Guide]({{ store_url }}/pages/concern-dullness): Explains the cellular reasons behind skin dullness and fatigue — impaired cell turnover, dehydration, oxidative stress — and how Aliangé resurfacing and brightening protocols restore luminosity and texture.
- [Redness & Sensitivity Guide]({{ store_url }}/pages/concern-redness): Clinical guide to persistent redness, reactive skin, and compromised barrier function. Details how Aliangé barrier-repair formulations reduce inflammation, calm reactivity, and rebuild skin resilience.
- [Skincare Protocol vs Routine — What's the Difference]({{ store_url }}/pages/skincare-protocol-vs-routine): Explains the clinical distinction between a skincare routine (random product stacking) and a skincare protocol (medically sequenced, synergistic system). Why protocols produce histological change and routines do not.
- [Ultimate Skincare Guide for Women Over 40]({{ store_url }}/pages/best-skincare-women-over-40-australia): Comprehensive doctor-led guide to skincare after 40 — hormonal skin changes, accelerated collagen loss, barrier thinning — and the best evidence-based Aliangé protocols for mature Australian skin.

